Very Funny Bunny Hop map made by me ( The Evil )
The map has 11 Levels of dificulty, and in the final have 3 especial rooms:
1 - Room with teleports to see the levels above.
2 - Room with 3 customizated Scouts with some especial efects
3 - Room with 2 bhop races to practice and enjoy with other friends who completed the map =]

Enjoy ;)


- Observation: I make maps in 1 or 2 years but this one is my first official and posted in one Website, plz rate it =D
